# RPCEmu derived / local files
#
# Build artefacts and locally-generated runtime files only.  Source that
# upstream ships (including the hand-written Makefiles under riscos-progs/
# and the default cmos.ram / rpc.cfg) is deliberately NOT ignored.

# --- Qt5 / qmake build artefacts (generated in src/qt5/) ---
/src/qt5/Makefile
/src/qt5/Makefile.Debug
/src/qt5/Makefile.Release
/src/qt5/.qmake.stash
/src/qt5/object_script.*
/src/qt5/release/
/src/qt5/debug/

# Compiled objects and qmake-generated sources (moc_*, qrc_*, ui_*)
*.o
moc_*.cpp
qrc_*.cpp
ui_*.h

# --- Built emulator binaries (qmake writes these to the repo root) ---
/rpcemu-interpreter*
/rpcemu-recompiler*
/RPCEmu-Interpreter*
/RPCEmu-Recompiler*

# --- Runtime-generated files ---
rpclog.txt

# CMOS NVRAM and GUI config: auto-generated with sensible defaults if absent
# (cmos_init() / config_load()), so kept local rather than tracked.  Shipped
# by upstream, so re-ignore these after a future RPCEmu import.
/cmos.ram
/rpc.cfg

# --- Local ROM and hard-disc images (large / copyrighted — never commit) ---
/roms/*.rom
*.hdf
